  <brief_title>Follow-up Study to Assess Safety and Clinical Activity of Continued AFFITOPE® AD02 Vaccinations of Patients Who Participated in AFF006</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Controlled, Parallel Group, Double-blind, Multi-centre, Phase IIb Study to Assess Safety and Clinical Activity of Continued AFFITOPE® AD02 Vaccinations of Patients Who Participated in the AFFITOPE® AD02 Phase II Study AFF006.</official_title>
