  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a follow-up study to assess safety and clinical activity of continued AFFITOPE® AD02
      vaccinations in patients with Alzheimer's disease. Patients, who have already participated in
      AFF006 will be involved in 27 study sites in Europe. Duration of patient's participation in
      the clinical trial is 19 months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
